Hey, I'm Kevin

I am a Full-Stack web developer with experience working in Python/Django, MERN, and C#/Asp.net

My Story:

After leaving home to join the airforce, I began my life journey in Alaska working in transportation. I spent the next 4 years there with 1 deployment to Qatar in the middle. When my time up in the military, I decided to continue my operations career in Seattle, WA. At the same time, I finished my Associate's degree in Transportation and Bachelor's in Business/International finance.

My whole life, I loved working with computers, creating awesome things out of nothing, automating & organizing operations, and creating my own art. I realized that I wasn't getting enough of that working in my feild of work and moving to Seattle helped me discover the world of computer programming. The Bellevue based school, Coding Dojo, has taught and prepared me to become a self-suficient, savvy, full-stack developer ready for anything thrown my way!
